| GET | `/api/v1/partners/{ulid}` | Partner state — full payload including recent contacts, open follow-ups |
| POST | `/api/v1/partners` | Upsert partner (idempotency-key required) |
| PATCH | `/api/v1/partners/{ulid}` | Update partner fields |
| DELETE | `/api/v1/partners/{ulid}` | Soft delete |
| POST | `/api/v1/partners/{ulid}/restore` | Restore |
| GET | `/api/v1/contacts` | List contacts; query params: `?partner_ulid=...&firm_ulid=...&from=...&to=...&limit=50` |
| POST | `/api/v1/contacts` | Log a contact (idempotency-key required) |
| GET | `/api/v1/contacts/{ulid}` | Single contact |
