### Component Architecture

Two layers:

**Layer 1 — Atomic UI components** (`web/src/components/ui/`):
- `Button.tsx` — Primary (Vermillion bg, Cool White text), Secondary (Slate Blue outline), Ghost (text-only).
- `Card.tsx` — White background, 4px radius, subtle Light Gray border, 24px padding.
- `Badge.tsx` — Small pill for tier/region labels.
- `StatusPill.tsx` — Coloured pill for relationship state. Cold = Light Gray, Warming = Slate Blue tinted, Warm = Slate Blue solid, Dormant = Dormant Gray, Overdue = Vermillion.
- `Timeline.tsx` — Vertical timeline for contact history.
- `DataTable.tsx` — Sortable, sticky-header table.
- `Sparkline.tsx` — Mini chart for contact activity (Recharts).
- `Input.tsx`, `Textarea.tsx`, `Select.tsx` — Form atoms.
- `Dialog.tsx` — Modal for create/edit forms.
- `EmptyState.tsx` — Illustration + message + CTA when no data.

**Layer 2 — Feature components** (`web/src/components/{dashboard,firm,partner,plan,audit}/`):
- `PipelineOverview.tsx` — Dashboard widget showing the 5 primary firms with sparklines.
- `UpcomingTouches.tsx` — Dashboard widget listing due/overdue contacts.
- `AuditHighlights.tsx` — Dashboard widget showing top audit actions.
- `FirmHeader.tsx`, `PartnerCard.tsx`, `ContactTimeline.tsx`, `FollowUpsList.tsx`.
- `LogContactForm.tsx` — The most-used form. Triggered from partner page; submits to `POST /api/v1/contacts`.
- `QuarterlyPlanGrid.tsx` — 4-card year view with current quarter expanded.

### Layout

App shell: top header (logo + nav + search box), no sidebar (kept clean per milanese-visual minimalism). Main content area centred at 1280px max width. Footer with small "Artemide v0.1" identifier and last-backup timestamp.

Header structure:
