## Deployment Sequence

1. Generate `ARTEMIDE_API_TOKEN` and `ARTEMIDE_COOKIE_SECRET` locally; store both in password manager.
2. Create Cloudflare Tunnel; obtain `TUNNEL_TOKEN`; configure route `artemide.francescofederico.net` → `http://artemide:8000`. Optional: add Cloudflare Access policy requiring Francesco's email for additional verification.
3. SSH to VPS; clone repo into `/opt/artemide/`.
4. Populate `.env` with all secrets.
5. `docker compose up -d` — multi-stage build runs (UI build, then API runtime), both services come up.
6. Verify health: `curl https://artemide.francescofederico.net/health` → 200 OK.
7. Seed: `docker compose exec artemide python scripts/seed_firms.py`.
8. Visit `https://artemide.francescofederico.net/login` in browser; enter token; verify dashboard loads.
9. Add MCP server in Claude.ai: URL `https://artemide.francescofederico.net/mcp`, header `Authorization: Bearer <token>`.
10. Test from Claude: "Show me my ledger state" → triggers audit_ledger, returns 11 seeded firms.
11. Configure cron on VPS for nightly backups.

