## Backup Strategy

Nightly `.backup` via host cron. SQLite handles concurrent reads during backup. Local retention 30 days. Off-site to R2 or private git highly recommended.

`scripts/backup.sh` script identical to v1.0 spec. `scripts/restore.sh` for rollback.

A "trigger now" button in the Settings UI calls a `POST /api/v1/admin/backup` endpoint that runs the same script synchronously and returns the resulting filename. Useful before any risky operation.

